*German: [[tatsächlich]] (1,3), [[konkret]] (1 ''case'', ''example''), [[gegenwärtig]] (2), [[aktuell]] (2)
*Spanish: [1,2] [[real]] [[:es:real|(es)]] 
*Vietnamese: [[đúng]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

